whereas.text:
Whereas, on May 3, 2003, the time-worn granite ledges of
			 the visage of the Old Man released their hold on the mountain and fell into
			 history;

Whereas the loss of the Old Man forever changed the face
			 of New Hampshire and was felt by all people of the State accustomed to living
			 under his watchful gaze;

Whereas the Old Man, who lived in the heart of the White
			 Mountains, now lives on in the hearts of the people of New Hampshire;
